### Features

#### Lightweight
µTorrent is a little over 1 MB (smaller than a digital photo!). It installs ultra-fast and will never hog your valuable system resources.

#### Powerful
Want total control? uTorrent offers advanced settings such as automation, scripting, remote management and more.

#### Fast
Download your files as quickly and efficiently as possible without slowing down your other online activities.

#### Download torrents in bulk
µTorrent Classic enables simultaneous torrent downloads that you can manage in a single location.

#### Optimize your bandwidth
µTorrent Classic auto-adjusts bandwidth usage, based on your network and internet connection, to ensure fast downloads.

#### Schedule your downloads
Set the day and time for your torrent downloads to start, stop or seed.

#### Remotely connect to µTorrent Classic
Add torrents to µTorrent Classic remotely from a web browser on any device.

[uTorrent Remote Instructions](https://remote.utorrent.com/signup)

